item.title: Can you
item.description:
@14-08 wrote:

Yes you can. But, you would have to do some work to make the interface appear. (I’m not even sure if this is what you mean). So, I think you mean the ‘Gnome Pilot’? If so, you would have to either make an interface that teleports you places. Or, if your source already has it, then you can just make said interface open when you talk to the Gnome Pilot.

Hope I helped…
